@startuml ICP CRUD Flow - Current

title ProspectOS Web - ICP CRUD Flow

actor User as U
participant "IcpsPage" as IP
participant "ICP API" as API

U -> IP: Open /icps
IP -> API: GET /api/icps
API --> IP: ICP list
IP --> U: Render table

== Create ==
U -> IP: Open create modal
U -> IP: Submit form
IP -> API: POST /api/icps
API --> IP: Created ICP
IP -> IP: invalidateQueries(["icps"])
IP --> U: Success feedback

== Update ==
U -> IP: Open edit modal
U -> IP: Submit changes
IP -> API: PUT /api/icps/{id}
API --> IP: Updated ICP
IP -> IP: invalidateQueries(["icps"])
IP --> U: Success feedback

== Delete ==
U -> IP: Confirm delete
IP -> API: DELETE /api/icps/{id}
API --> IP: 204 No Content
IP -> IP: invalidateQueries(["icps"])
IP --> U: Success feedback

@enduml
